title: iPhone sales less than expected, but Apple points to the good news
text:
iPhone sales less than expected, but Apple points to the good news Thursday, February 01, 2018 - 01:21 
The iPhones don't seem to be flying off the shelves as fast as Wall Street predicted, but that's not stopping Apple from patting itself on the back for a record holiday quarter sales.
